<br>
See if you can slide your desk a little farther away from the wall so you can back your moniter up, to slide your keyboard farther up also. <br>
<br>
I have allways thought that them eurgo-Keyboards were ghey looking, but they might be sometihng for you to look at if your feeling pain. <br>
<br>
<br>
Don't let it hut you. <br>
<br>
<br>
I hope some of this can help some of you. <br>
<br>
